title: [Orcswold, Wooded Trail]
description: The trail curves sharply over the top of a small ridge, sloping down steeply to the southeast.  Patches of delicate wildflowers are sprinkled beneath the ominous canopy of branches, seeming somehow out of place next to the clawed footprints that have trampled their borders.

The trail curves sharply over the top of a small ridge, sloping down steeply to the southeast.  Patches of delicate wildflowers glow faintly in the moonlight beneath the ominous canopy of branches, seeming somehow out of place next to the clawed footprints that have trampled their borders.
